    "believe": {
      "description": "Belief dispatch. Arms are evaluated in order; the first arm whose condition is truthy returns its value. The subject is bound to the local name ``it`` inside every arm and inside ``else``. The ``else`` arm is required; partial belief dispatch is a structural error.",
